{
  "texts": [
    "• MTP foot_58.",
    "The full name of MTP is Massive Text Pairs, comprising a total of 300M aligned Chinese-English text pairs.",
    "It serves as a crucial foundation for training Chinese-English semantic vector models.",
    "• MultiUN (Eisele and Chen, 2010).",
    "The MultiUN corpus is sourced from files within the United Nations Official Document System."
  ]
}